## Next Steps
* **MP-TE Workshop**: A hands-on lab workshop is planned for October to allow service providers to test and provide feedback on the CLI and telemetry aspects of the MP-TE implementation.
* **Multicast TE (MC-TE)**: The authors plan to refine the MC-TE signaling details, prepare prototype implementations, and present a more detailed comparison against RFC 4875 at the next IETF meeting.